trans-unit.source: Encapsulates basic validation rules that indicate whether a piece of custom data is considered personalizable in either <see cref="F:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope.User" /> or <see cref="F:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope.Shared" /> scope.
trans-unit.target: Encapsula reglas de validación básicas que indican si un dato personalizado se considera personalizable en un ámbito <see cref="F:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope.User" /> o <see cref="F:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope.Shared" />.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationDictionary> instance is a collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationEntry> objects, which consist of a personalization scope and an object value.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationDictionary> instancia es una colección de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationEntry> objetos, que constan de un ámbito de personalización y un valor del objeto.

trans-unit.source: These entries are assigned a key in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationDictionary> object.
trans-unit.target: Estas entradas se asignan a una clave en el <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationDictionary> objeto.

trans-unit.source: A good practice is to add all properties to the dictionary using the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IPersonalizable.Save%2A> method, regardless of the scope of the page.
trans-unit.target: Una práctica recomendada consiste en Agregar todas las propiedades al diccionario utilizando la <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IPersonalizable.Save%2A> método, independientemente del ámbito de la página.

trans-unit.source: The .NET Framework saves the information in the appropriate way; for example, shared data is saved when the page is in <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope.Shared> scope.
trans-unit.target: .NET Framework guarda la información de la manera adecuada; Por ejemplo, se guardan los datos compartidos cuando la página está en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope.Shared> ámbito.

trans-unit.source: However, shared properties are not saved when a Web Parts value is being saved, the page is in <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope.User> scope, and the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control was added with the page in <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope.Shared> scope.
trans-unit.target: Sin embargo, las propiedades compartidas no se guardan cuando se guarda un valor de elementos Web, la página está en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope.User> ámbito y la <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control se agregó a la página de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope.Shared> ámbito.

trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationDictionary" />.

trans-unit.target: Agrega entradas de personalización al diccionario de personalización.

trans-unit.source: You can call this method, place various pieces of custom state information into the state object, and specify the scope associated with the state value.
trans-unit.target: Puede llamar a este método, colocar diversos elementos de información de estado personalizada en el objeto de estado y especificar el ámbito asociado con el valor de estado.

trans-unit.source: When a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control is in <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope.Shared> scope, you can add name and state information that is associated with either <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope.Shared> scope or <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope.User> scope.
trans-unit.target: Cuando un <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control se encuentra en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope.Shared> ámbito, puede agregar información de nombre y estada asociada <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope.Shared> ámbito o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope.User> ámbito.

trans-unit.source: In <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope.User> scope, you can add name and state information associated only with <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope.User> scope.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope.User> ámbito, puede agregar información de nombre y estada asociada únicamente al <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope.User> ámbito.

trans-unit.source: It is a good practice, however, to add all properties to the dictionary using <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IPersonalizable.Save%2A> including properties with <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope.User> or <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope.Shared> scope, regardless of the scope of the page.
trans-unit.target: Es una buena práctica, sin embargo, para agregar todas las propiedades al diccionario mediante <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IPersonalizable.Save%2A> incluidas las propiedades con <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope.User> o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope.Shared> ámbito, independientemente del ámbito de la página.

trans-unit.source: The .NET Framework only saves the properties with <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope.Shared> scope when appropriate.
trans-unit.target: .NET Framework sólo guarda las propiedades con <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope.Shared> ámbito cuando corresponda.

trans-unit.source: In other words, shared properties are not saved when a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control that was initially added in <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope.Shared> scope is later saved while the page is in <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope.User> scope.
trans-unit.target: En otras palabras, comparten propiedades no se guardan cuando un <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control que se agregó inicialmente en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope.Shared> ámbito se guarda después mientras la página está en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope.User> ámbito.

trans-unit.source: In an opposite scenario, if a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control was added to the page in <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope.User> scope, and the control is later saved while the page is in <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope.Shared> scope, custom shared property values are saved (along with custom user-scoped properties).
trans-unit.target: En un escenario opuesto, si un <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control se agregó a la página de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope.User> ámbito y el control se guarda después mientras la página está en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope.Shared> ámbito, se guardan los valores de propiedad compartida personalizada (junto con las propiedades de ámbito de usuario personalizados).

trans-unit.source: For details on personalization data and how shared and user-scoped properties are affected by the personalization scope of the page, see the [Web Parts Personalization Overview](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/7dc34f74-52aa-4082-b98d-2bcf9e07e320) topic.
trans-unit.target: Para obtener más información sobre los datos de personalización y las propiedades de modo compartidas y en el ámbito de usuario se ven afectadas por el ámbito de personalización de la página, consulte la [Web Parts Personalization Overview](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/7dc34f74-52aa-4082-b98d-2bcf9e07e320) tema.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationDictionary.Add%2A> method checks several details to ensure the validity of `value` and `key` before attempting to add them to the personalization dictionary.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationDictionary.Add%2A> método comprueba varios detalles para garantizar la validez de `value` y `key` antes de intentar agregarlos al diccionario de personalización.

trans-unit.source: If the checks are successful, the method calls the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationDictionary> class's own <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationDictionary.Add%2A> method, passing to it the `key` and `value` parameters.
trans-unit.target: Si las comprobaciones son correctas, el método llama a la <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationDictionary> la clase <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationDictionary.Add%2A> método, pasándole el `key` y `value` parámetros.

trans-unit.target: Es <see langword="true" /> si <paramref name="key" /> existe en el diccionario de personalización; de lo contrario, es <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationDictionary.Contains%2A> method checks `key` to ensure it is a valid object for checking the personalization dictionary, and if so, it passes it to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationDictionary> class's own <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationDictionary.Contains%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationDictionary.Contains%2A> método comprueba `key` para asegurarse de es un objeto válido para comprobar el diccionario de personalización y, si es así, pasa a la <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationDictionary> la clase <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationDictionary.Contains%2A> método.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationDictionary.Item%2A> first ensures that `key` is a <xref:System.String> object, and if so, it calls the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationDictionary> class's own <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationDictionary.Item%2A> property to return the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationEntry> whose key equals `key` in the current dictionary.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationDictionary.Item%2A> garantiza que, en primer lugar `key` es un <xref:System.String> objeto, y por lo tanto, llama a la <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationDictionary> la clase <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationDictionary.Item%2A> propiedad para devolver el <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationEntry> cuya clave es igual a `key` en el diccionario actual.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="key" /> is not a <see cref="T:System.String" /> object.

trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationDictionary.Remove%2A> método comprueba si `key` es un <xref:System.String> objeto, y por lo tanto, llama a la <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationDictionary> la clase <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationDictionary.Remove%2A> método, pasando `key` a él.
